{"1":[[425,491,"Oscar!"],[748,898,"Save our baby."],[1008,1078,"Save you?"],[1126,1238,"I told you,"],[1328,1456,"I swapped your folic acid"],[1456,1592,"with slow-acting poison."],[1655,1854,"That made you miscarry and bleed out."],[2166,2266,"Why?!"],[2312,2495,"You scheming b**ch!"],[2607,2864,"If you hadn't run your mouth off to Grandpa,"],[2864,3064,"I could've married your sister Luna!"],[3072,3220,"She wouldn't be sent abroad."],[3347,3607,"You brought all this on yourself."],[3720,3924,"That was your baby!"],[4364,4532,"You don't deserve to have my child!"],[6258,6336,"Brother-in-law."],[6367,6444,"Oh no."],[6504,6777,"Guess I should call you hubby now."],[6779,6839,"Luna."],[6895,7115,"From now on, you're my wife,"],[7201,7301,"the lady of the Russel family."],[7388,7580,"You two are shameless!"],[7668,7824,"You killed my baby!"],[8072,8108,"Doctor."],[8152,8268,"Sign off on the cremation now."],[8324,8392,"I'm busy."],[8406,8454,"Wait!"],[8866,8954,"It's him."],[8996,9160,"Oscar's brother, Lucian Russel."],[9680,9720,"Doctor."],[9842,9937,"Please save her."],[9983,10053,"Mr. Russel."],[10079,10224,"She's gone. We can't save her."],[10225,10319,"Please save her!"],[10336,10472,"She… she can't be saved."],[10484,10644,"She's… she's gone."],[11112,11216,"Oscar."],[11398,11450,"Back then…"],[11450,11561,"I never should've let her marry you."],[11612,11772,"Or what, marry a cripple like you?"],[11813,11984,"Lucian, get this straight."],[12041,12185,"She's your sister-in-law."],[12193,12293,"Cops already have evidence"],[12330,12438,"that you murdered her."],[12493,12589,"Rot in prison"],[12612,12740,"for the rest of your life."],[12776,12820,"Lucian Russel!"],[12821,12957,"You can't frame me like this!"],[12966,13119,"Aurora's just unlucky,"],[13174,13278,"it's not my fault!"],[13824,13992,"If I had a second shot at life,"],[14064,14248,"I'd never make the same mistake."],[15300,15376,"Aurora."],[15507,15583,"Aurora."],[16752,16816,"Well…"],[16860,16948,"Who will you choose?"],[17013,17097,"(This was the day Zack)"],[17098,17251,"(asked me to choose a husband.)"],[17304,17349,"(Could it be…)"],[17383,17488,"(Was I reborn?)"]],"2":[[60,115,"Aurora."],[173,237,"Back in the War,"],[240,366,"your grandpa and I"],[384,543,"made a pact for our families."],[612,796,"Now you're twenty years old."],[821,965,"You can choose one of"],[967,1116,"my grandsons to marry."],[1201,1249,"Well?"],[1315,1510,"Who will you choose?"],[1957,2059,"You've decided?"],[2094,2178,"Him?"],[2396,2483,"Yes, him."],[2494,2542,"Good."],[2564,2748,"You'll stay at our villa for now."],[2810,2954,"Tomorrow is your birthday."],[3007,3250,"I booked you a party at a live house."],[3274,3442,"It's popular among you folks now, right?"],[3525,3704,"Have a great time."],[3887,4000,"Thank you, Zack."],[5120,5210,"Why are you here again?"],[5247,5331,"She's certainly here"],[5356,5528,"for you, Oscar."],[5644,5708,"Aurora."],[5761,5837,"You really go all out"],[5837,5960,"when chasing a man."],[5981,6073,"If your late grandpa knew"],[6100,6276,"you were being so forward,"],[6278,6367,"I wonder if"],[6399,6580,"he'd think you're a disgrace."],[6890,6958,"Aurora."],[7079,7211,"You're here again to say"],[7243,7376,"your grandpa once saved mine"],[7376,7490,"on the battlefield, right?"],[7496,7618,"This \"guilt tripping\" card"],[7631,7762,"is getting real old."],[7805,7928,"Wake up."],[7968,8057,"You've made our business"],[8059,8173,"the talk of the town."],[8204,8368,"You've ruined my reputation."],[8424,8548,"I'm still considering our marriage."],[8593,8717,"Begging won't help."],[9478,9628,"Zack asked me to come."],[9671,9866,"He said he's throwing me a party tomorrow."],[10092,10314,"Grandpa's hosting your birthday party?"],[10392,10471,"He hasn't meddled"],[10472,10597,"in family matters for ages."],[10615,10799,"Yet he's throwing Aurora a party."],[10821,10925,"Could the rumor be true?"],[10958,11058,"Whoever marries Aurora"],[11086,11194,"will inherit the family business"],[11209,11329,"and become the Russels' head?"],[11439,11535,"Congrats, Oscar."],[11543,11607,"Hey, make sure you"],[11633,11800,"look out for us in the future!"],[11804,11895,"With Grandpa's support,"],[11900,12100,"Oscar can finally shine."],[12120,12315,"Aurora, congrats to you too."],[12335,12487,"You finally got what you wanted."],[12531,12707,"You must be thrilled."],[12764,12843,"But—"],[13490,13574,"Let's get this straight."],[13656,13803,"After we get married,"],[13803,13940,"don't meddle in my affairs."],[13980,14259,"Only then will I agree to marry you."],[14447,14605,"(I must've been out of my mind.)"],[14659,14756,"(How did I fall for)"],[14759,14911,"(a man like this in my last life?)"],[14930,15024,"Hey, Sis!"]],"3":[[0,100,"Hey, Sis!"],[431,514,"Aurora..."],[758,966,"Why'd you come out when you're sick?"],[985,1089,"Oscar."],[1111,1296,"Dad told me to come with her."],[1311,1424,"He didn't want her alone."],[1533,1611,"Brother-in-law."],[1663,1744,"Oh no."],[1792,2080,"I should call you hubby now."],[2140,2188,"Luna."],[2295,2365,"From now on,"],[2365,2516,"you'll be my wife."],[2559,2683,"The lady of the Russel family."],[3117,3237,"What are you, a little kid?"],[3272,3401,"Still need her to follow you outside?"],[3509,3645,"You believe all she says?"],[3828,3992,"Why would Luna lie?"],[4003,4061,"I'm warning you,"],[4062,4110,"Aurora."],[4121,4195,"If you keep"],[4197,4347,"being so selfish and willful,"],[4405,4572,"I won't marry you."],[5003,5128,"You're that sure"],[5210,5342,"I'll marry you?"],[5838,5967,"Duh, of course."],[6029,6164,"You follow me like a lapdog"],[6164,6243,"every single day."],[6243,6311,"If you won't marry me,"],[6311,6420,"who else will you marry!"],[7398,7492,"Who's she?"],[7492,7649,"She's the granddaughter of Sir Russel's friend."],[7651,7733,"She's stunning."],[7734,7851,"Like a movie star."],[7941,8176,"Such poise and elegance,"],[8197,8297,"graceful and refined."],[8519,8644,"Excuse me, please."],[8715,8787,"Miss Quinn."],[8800,8965,"This is a birthday gift from Mr. Lucian."],[8995,9125,"Happy birthday."],[10488,10540,"Thank you."],[10540,10600,"Mm."],[10960,11036,"Aurora."],[11126,11218,"Happy birthday."],[11340,11512,"I wonder what gift"],[11543,11736,"Oscar got for you."],[11759,11823,"After all,"],[11823,11987,"he's your fiancé."],[12154,12293,"Yeah, Aurora."],[12335,12523,"Why isn't Oscar here?"],[13084,13158,"Hey, Sis."],[13255,13367,"Happy birthday."],[13517,13597,"Just now,"],[13647,13870,"Oscar told me in the bedroom"],[14061,14271,"I'm the woman he loves most."]],"4":[[17,167,"Just now, in the bedroom"],[172,275,"Oscar told me"],[524,696,"I'm the woman he loves most."],[908,1020,"What are you doing?"],[1072,1224,"Why are you so jumpy?"],[1391,1451,"Luna."],[1567,1683,"Your lipstick…"],[1778,1865,"is smudged."],[2407,2479,"(This woman…)"],[2481,2664,"(Why is she different now?)"],[2896,2949,"Aurora."],[3067,3183,"Are you playing nice"],[3218,3401,"'cause you're scared"],[3403,3552,"I might not marry you?"],[3641,3720,"But then again,"],[3803,3911,"I, Oscar Russel,"],[3914,4124,"will soon be the Russel family's head."],[4177,4397,"I can't have just one woman."],[4447,4639,"I'll have countless lovers."],[4921,5079,"Since you're so obedient today,"],[5131,5203,"I'll reward you."],[5498,5632,"So pretty!"],[5688,5920,"Isn't this Cartier's new bracelet?"],[5971,6147,"It's so hard to get it."],[6292,6392,"Like it, Luna?"],[6540,6651,"Then it's yours."],[6923,7000,"Forget it."],[7059,7143,"Didn't you buy"],[7143,7315,"this gift for my sister?"],[7368,7623,"I can't just take it from her."],[7654,7728,"So what?"],[7740,7843,"If you like it, take it."],[7912,7984,"As for Aurora,"],[8064,8278,"I'll just find her something else."],[8404,8484,"Really?"],[8515,8643,"Then I won't hold back."],[8923,8987,"Sis,"],[9040,9223,"you're not mad, right?"],[9528,9651,"Gifts from him?"],[9743,9871,"I don't care for them."],[10002,10054,"Aurora,"],[10090,10238,"why act all high and mighty?"],[10279,10420,"I remember once, in the rain,"],[10471,10584,"you were soaked."],[10584,10768,"I lent you my old jacket."],[10849,10941,"But, when I wasn't looking,"],[10959,11100,"you sniffed my clothes."],[11171,11231,"What?"],[11259,11315,"Aurora,"],[11315,11462,"you're just my lapdog."],[11464,11571,"You got it wrong."],[11612,11715,"I just thought"],[11715,11856,"the perfume on your jacket"],[11876,11979,"smelled cheap…"],[12035,12151,"and disgusting."],[12292,12379,"That upsets you?"],[12431,12559,"Ha! Look at you!"],[12615,12687,"I knew it—"],[12687,12830,"a vicious b**ch like you"],[12843,12968,"couldn't be that generous!"],[13107,13231,"Show some respect!"],[13253,13309,"Respect?"],[13336,13438,"What respect?"],[13480,13584,"Weren't you desperate"],[13584,13675,"to marry me?"],[13747,13936,"We'll be in the same bed anyway."],[13963,14055,"Why pretend?"],[14102,14212,"You're that sure"],[14251,14347,"I'll marry you?"]],"5":[[44,128,"If you won't marry me,"],[128,216,"who will you marry?"],[268,396,"You've loved me so much."],[455,528,"What—"],[608,748,"you'd rather marry someone else?"],[787,848,"Besides,"],[872,1008,"the only other man in my family"],[1132,1211,"is my brother Lucian."],[1259,1341,"But,"],[1419,1580,"he had a car accident before."],[1596,1732,"Almost ended up paralyzed."],[1764,1928,"He's been sickly ever since."],[1948,2003,"Plus,"],[2044,2260,"he might be a little 'damaged' downstairs."],[2287,2380,"If you marry him,"],[2392,2531,"you'll be a widow for sure."],[2851,3000,"(Since you chose him,)"],[3019,3100,"(I'll honor your choice.)"],[3151,3271,"(Don't tell anyone yet.)"],[3307,3464,"(When things settle down,)"],[3475,3675,"(the truth will come out anyways.)"],[4056,4188,"Damaged? You mean…"],[4256,4377,"This part?!"],[4435,4484,"Ah!"],[4678,4925,"(She… she's defending me?)"],[4944,4992,"You—"],[5185,5256,"Oscar."],[5471,5556,"Lucian is here?"],[5756,5884,"So what?"],[5935,6067,"What I said was true."],[6142,6234,"Lucian needs"],[6263,6455,"a wheelchair to get around."],[6487,6592,"Not to mention other things."],[6707,6756,"Oscar,"],[6820,6887,"today is Grandpa's"],[6887,7028,"birthday banquet for Aurora."],[7084,7320,"This isn't the place to cause a scene."],[9415,9487,"Hey, Sis."],[9600,9779,"Oscar couldn't make it."],[9900,10031,"You don't mind"],[10071,10243,"if I ride with you, right?"],[11340,11558,"Aurora, even if you marry Oscar,"],[11558,11623,"so what?"],[11707,11931,"You'll never get his heart."],[13019,13140,"If I can't have his heart,"],[13200,13347,"why would I want him?"],[13406,13550,"I hope you get to marry him soon."],[13628,13752,"So I can wish you two—"],[13940,14047,"a lifetime of unity."],[14071,14203,"And eternal bliss."],[14324,14403,"What do you mean?"],[14587,14689,"(This time,)"],[14726,14890,"(I'll let you have Oscar.)"],[14974,15196,"(Let's see how that ends for you.)"]],"6":[[0,200,"I know you're just playing it cool."],[260,404,"But regardless,"],[455,612,"the one Oscar loves—"],[816,964,"is me."],[1472,1527,"Hey, Dad."],[1531,1587,"Aurora."],[1619,1712,"It's Mid-Autumn Festival."],[1739,1832,"When you go see Zack,"],[1832,1948,"send him my greetings."],[1992,2094,"Also, when you're there,"],[2107,2216,"if you see your sister Luna,"],[2219,2365,"tell her to come home soon."],[2371,2494,"She's been gone for days."],[2498,2580,"Got it, Dad."],[2735,2776,"Bye."],[3788,3856,"Sis."],[3867,4092,"Doesn't this outfit look great?"],[4139,4243,"Oscar bought"],[4243,4332,"all of it for me."],[4516,4724,"He said only I deserve these."],[4759,4839,"Good for you."],[4928,4975,"Hey…"],[5072,5166,"Sis."],[5207,5396,"Why are you being so cold?"],[5432,5532,"I just wanted"],[5532,5664,"to share my happiness."],[5793,5873,"I see."],[5924,6034,"You're jealous."],[6085,6228,"But when it comes to love,"],[6279,6386,"no one can help it."],[6435,6476,"Move."],[6520,6656,"You're wasting my time."],[6706,6738,"Ouch!"],[6890,6942,"Sis."],[6943,7071,"Why did you hit me?"],[7131,7276,"I'm your sister!"],[7323,7476,"Aurora, what are you doing?"],[7576,7682,"Oscar!"],[8229,8277,"Aurora."],[8315,8379,"Is this how"],[8379,8492,"you treat your little sister?"],[8507,8668,"Have you no decency?"],[8749,8900,"Is that Miss Quinn?"],[9058,9161,"She's bullying her own sister"],[9179,9329,"just to win over a man?"],[9484,9676,"What a disgrace."],[9723,9800,"Exactly."],[9851,10048,"She looks sweet on the outside,"],[10076,10326,"but she's got a heart of ice."],[10536,10600,"Luna Quinn."],[10623,10784,"Didn't think at your age"],[10812,10984,"you'd learn such low tricks."],[11110,11206,"You dare scold Luna?!"]],"7":[[0,176,"(This is the Russel family's banquet,)"],[191,312,"(the guests are all high-profile.)"],[312,432,"(I can't embarrass Zack)"],[432,524,"(and ruin it.)"],[535,620,"I heard she's getting"],[620,779,"engaged to a Russel grandson today."],[807,942,"Marrying a woman like that,"],[980,1198,"the Russels are done for."],[1201,1375,"Can't wait to watch it go down."],[1475,1527,"Aurora."],[1629,1719,"Right now,"],[1771,1912,"apologize to Luna."],[2003,2096,"How did I end up"],[2096,2192,"with a woman like you?"],[2262,2359,"Such bad luck."],[2397,2461,"Miss Quinn,"],[2507,2595,"if you can't even"],[2603,2703,"tolerate your own sister,"],[2703,2807,"how about others?"],[2883,2951,"Oscar will"],[2953,3086,"have other women later."],[3092,3235,"Will you act like a shrew then?"],[3298,3377,"Maybe…"],[3392,3511,"Miss Quinn here"],[3513,3728,"can fight off every woman in town."],[3739,4011,"Drive them all away from Oscar."],[4107,4232,"(Back then, for Oscar,)"],[4232,4339,"(I learned martial arts.)"],[4400,4456,"(I even said,)"],[4456,4653,"(I'll fight whoever tries to steal Oscar.)"],[4720,4807,"(Now that I think about it,)"],[4807,4915,"(it's embarrassing.)"],[5188,5364,"Today Grandpa will announce"],[5364,5471,"our engagement."],[5639,5784,"If you want to marry me,"],[5811,5928,"then like I said before,"],[6071,6311,"after we get married, don't interfere"],[6356,6435,"with my life."],[6456,6556,"If you agree,"],[6576,6679,"I'll forgive"],[6679,6812,"your viciousness and arrogance."],[7015,7135,"You're shameless."],[7179,7312,"After Oscar marries,"],[7315,7456,"he'll be the Russel family's head."],[7487,7635,"We'll all rely on him."],[7664,7782,"With such a big business,"],[7843,7971,"he needs a capable wife."],[7997,8053,"That's right."],[8064,8159,"If you ask me,"],[8200,8358,"women are just playthings,"],[8368,8531,"easy to control, easy to toss."],[8615,8704,"After today,"],[8740,8920,"I'll inherit the Russel Group."],[8920,9015,"If you obey,"],[9068,9130,"I won't let you"],[9131,9228,"lose face in public."],[9783,9863,"So—"],[9951,10012,"you,"],[10116,10304,"apologize to Luna right now!"],[10602,10726,"What's all this ruckus?"],[10900,10995,"It's a banquet,"],[11012,11201,"you trying to upset Sir Russel?!"]],"8":[[191,264,"Aurora."],[304,383,"You okay?"],[491,563,"(Last life…)"],[571,704,"(He never called me sister-in-law.)"],[771,959,"(I always thought he didn't accept me.)"],[1016,1091,"(Not until I died)"],[1091,1216,"(did I realize that wasn't true.)"],[1378,1438,"Does it hurt?"],[1683,1745,"No."],[1930,2012,"Whether she hurts"],[2012,2132,"is none of your business."],[2184,2232,"Lucian,"],[2283,2432,"she's your future sister-in-law."],[2483,2532,"What?"],[2578,2739,"You wanna get with her?"],[2966,3260,"After Lucian's car accident"],[3270,3432,"I heard he couldn't get it up."],[3460,3507,"Lucian,"],[3550,3643,"it's an important banquet."],[3684,3852,"why aren't you in your room,"],[3871,4047,"instead of embarassing yourself here?"],[4156,4215,"Your sister-in-law"],[4235,4379,"follows me like a dog every day,"],[4388,4500,"clinging to me."],[4524,4647,"When the owner scolds his dog,"],[4720,4767,"what,"],[4812,4900,"you gonna butt in too?"],[4911,4984,"Oscar Russel,"],[5060,5171,"Aurora is a person,"],[5206,5371,"not a pet or an object."],[5435,5556,"As for being a disgrace,"],[5619,5703,"your behavior"],[5732,5888,"brings shame to this family!"],[5894,5934,"You—"],[6219,6328,"Forget it, Lucian."],[6381,6495,"He's not worth it."],[6731,6782,"Miss Quinn,"],[6784,6831,"let's go."],[6869,6941,"Sir Russel is here."],[6998,7040,"Let's go."],[7370,7687,"Don't forget what I told you."]],"9":[[175,391,"Today is a great day."],[391,536,"Thank you all for coming"],[536,769,"to the Russel family's banquet."],[1075,1259,"Now, I'll announce something."],[1259,1383,"My old friend's granddaughter—"],[1383,1459,"Aurora Quinn."],[1459,1551,"She is now 20 years old."],[1556,1727,"According to our agreement,"],[1733,1919,"she will choose one of my grandsons"],[1922,2076,"to be her husband."],[2076,2180,"After the wedding,"],[2191,2318,"I will give them"],[2319,2515,"80% of my personal assets"],[2518,2667,"to inherit the Russel Group."],[2730,2928,"They will run our family empire."],[3207,3356,"Sir Russel's wealth"],[3356,3484,"is a mystery."],[3484,3632,"Even 20% or 30%—"],[3632,3767,"not to mention 80%—"],[3767,3852,"is a fortune"],[3852,3988,"no ordinary person could earn."],[3996,4128,"Whoever marries Aurora"],[4128,4200,"is truly blessed."],[4203,4300,"Exactly."],[4400,4646,"Now, let's have Aurora come up"],[4675,4888,"and announce her chosen groom."],[4896,5064,"Let everyone be the witness."],[5064,5115,"Good."],[5115,5279,"Good!"],[6032,6164,"Everyone already knows"],[6164,6296,"she's gonna choose Oscar."],[6296,6396,"What's there to announce?"],[6396,6435,"Alas."],[6464,6643,"It's about inheritance—"],[6684,6815,"it has to be made public."],[6815,6956,"A few days ago,"],[6956,7222,"I had a long, long nightmare."],[7223,7340,"When I woke up,"],[7340,7484,"I understood something."],[7500,7623,"If someone keeps chasing"],[7623,7812,"a person who doesn't love them,"],[7812,7971,"they'll go astray"],[7971,8095,"and lose themselves."],[8128,8240,"A healthy relationship"],[8240,8496,"should be like two trees—"],[8543,8676,"roots together,"],[8720,8906,"but each growing freely."],[9015,9076,"True love"],[9114,9243,"may arrive suddenly."],[9401,9504,"When I turned around,"],[9535,9623,"I realized"],[9623,9786,"he was always by my side."],[9842,10022,"So, the man I choose to marry is—"],[10100,10340,"Lucian Russel."],[10340,10456,"That's impossible!"]],"10":[[0,84,"That's impossible!"],[115,212,"I thought Aurora was"],[212,320,"crazy in love with Oscar."],[320,424,"Why choose Lucian?"],[487,604,"Grandpa,"],[604,740,"this must be a mistake."],[763,843,"You child—"],[859,967,"so young,"],[967,1116,"yet your ears are worse than mine."],[1116,1316,"She said it loud and clear."],[1335,1435,"Lucian Russel."],[1491,1628,"How could that be a mistake?"],[1745,1832,"Aurora."],[1871,1960,"You misspoke,"],[1960,2028,"didn't you?"],[2028,2164,"The one you love is me."],[2176,2355,"The man I choose to marry is—"],[2355,2491,"Lucian Russel."],[2714,2794,"Impossible."],[3003,3123,"The one you love is me."],[3123,3211,"It's me!"],[3211,3332,"The whole city knows"],[3332,3492,"Lucian is a cripple,"],[3492,3609,"a sickly invalid!"],[3667,3790,"Let me go!"],[4020,4103,"I get it—"],[4103,4232,"you're mad at me, right?"],[4239,4311,"You're mad"],[4311,4428,"I gave your birthday gift"],[4428,4520,"to Luna."],[4546,4594,"Huh?"],[5171,5320,"Give it to me."],[5478,5586,"Oscar…"],[5792,5939,"I don't want something"],[5977,6057,"someone else wore."],[6243,6332,"I know you're"],[6333,6445,"just throwing a fit,"],[6492,6551,"aren't you?"],[6571,6664,"It's fine."],[6664,6807,"I can buy you a new one."],[6830,6920,"I don't need it."],[6920,7048,"You're just jealous,"],[7112,7179,"so you"],[7212,7377,"chose Lucian to spite me."],[7392,7448,"Oscar,"],[7464,7595,"why would you say that?"],[7595,7796,"I've only ever seen you as a brother."],[7840,7934,"Brother?"],[8068,8224,"You're calling me brother?"],[8274,8452,"The one you love is clearly me!"],[8495,8708,"Lucian is just a cripple!"],[8795,8892,"Nonsense!"],[8892,8986,"You brat—"],[9004,9176,"how can you speak of your brother that way?"],[9214,9314,"Grandpa—"],[9337,9568,"Aurora and I grew up together,"],[9568,9752,"childhood sweethearts in love."],[9763,9904,"You can't break us apart!"],[9935,10079,"Childhood sweethearts?"],[10091,10220,"Mutual love?"],[10220,10392,"That's not what I know."],[10392,10464,"Aurora,"],[10482,10602,"tell us yourself."]],"11":[[0,72,"Aurora."],[84,187,"Tell us yourself."],[198,270,"Grandpa,"],[283,383,"I don't know why Oscar"],[383,513,"would say such things."],[522,612,"I've only ever treated him"],[612,763,"like an older brother."],[802,878,"Besides—"],[903,1102,"the one he loves is my sister Luna,"],[1132,1219,"not me."],[1280,1411,"That's not true, Grandpa!"],[1496,1580,"Aurora,"],[1596,1712,"the one I love is you."],[1712,1875,"You're the only one I love!"],[1879,1976,"Oscar,"],[2049,2282,"didn't you say I was the only one you love?"],[2285,2476,"You said my sister clung to you every day"],[2476,2614,"and you were sick of her."],[2630,2735,"Don't touch me!"],[2739,2876,"You're Aurora's sister,"],[2880,2983,"and I'm your brother-in-law."],[2983,3148,"Don't you dare put words in my mouth!"],[3148,3300,"How could you—"],[3591,3759,"treat me like this?"],[3975,4032,"Aurora,"],[4032,4134,"problem solved."],[4156,4300,"You can only be engaged to me."],[4407,4515,"You can only love me now."],[4524,4665,"I don't love you now—"],[4685,4837,"and I never will."],[5015,5145,"You're mad because I hit you, huh?"],[5171,5248,"It's fine."],[5332,5408,"Here!"],[5442,5582,"hit me. Hit me."],[5632,5814,"If you forgive me, I'll take anything."],[5815,5932,"Don't touch me!"],[5967,6016,"Fine,"],[6035,6147,"I'll do it myself."],[6164,6284,"If it makes you forgive me,"],[6343,6455,"I'll do anything."],[6971,7071,"Ow…"],[7100,7215,"This—"],[7343,7535,"You disgraceful thing!"],[7535,7607,"Guards!"],[7607,7687,"Take him out!"],[7776,7848,"Mr. Oscar."],[7864,7952,"Don't touch me!"],[8195,8271,"Aurora,"],[8292,8448,"say you made a mistake."],[8456,8600,"You do love me!"],[9264,9339,"Oscar."],[9365,9540,"Many important eyes are watching."],[9540,9607,"Stop this."],[9679,9740,"Aurora"],[9764,9871,"has already chosen me."]],"12":[[0,56,"Aurora"],[80,187,"has already chosen me."],[187,343,"Who do you think you are?"],[343,528,"You don't deserve to speak to me!"],[528,659,"What about me?"],[720,864,"Do I deserve it?"],[896,959,"Grandpa!"],[959,1083,"You insolent brat!"],[1083,1175,"Starting today,"],[1175,1291,"don't go to the company."],[1291,1427,"Stay home and reflect!"],[1435,1519,"Aurora,"],[1519,1648,"tell Grandpa quickly—"],[1648,1776,"the one you love is me!"],[1792,1844,"It's me!"],[1892,1976,"Oscar,"],[2016,2123,"what are you saying?"],[2132,2232,"I truly don't understand."],[2235,2403,"I heard before"],[2407,2464,"that Aurora"],[2464,2587,"loved Mr. Oscar."],[2587,2676,"But now it seems—"],[2676,2796,"that's not the case."],[2796,2883,"Exactly."],[2887,3109,"He probably just spread that rumor"],[3112,3239,"to secure the inheritance."],[3239,3417,"That's so low of Oscar."],[3428,3511,"So he deliberately"],[3511,3628,"ruined a girl's reputation?"],[3664,3747,"Men like that"],[3747,3896,"are truly dangerous."],[3896,4011,"I'm gonna warn my friends"],[4011,4160,"to blacklist him."],[4264,4496,"It's not like that!"],[4552,4696,"The one Aurora loves is me!"],[4711,4807,"It's me!"],[4903,4984,"Aurora,"],[4984,5143,"if you're having regrets,"],[5171,5271,"I'll go to Grandpa"],[5352,5439,"and ask him to cancel the engagement."],[5479,5615,"Why would I regret it?"],[5632,5734,"I know,"],[5762,5835,"you..."],[6007,6132,"Back then I was obsessed"],[6247,6388,"with something I couldn't have."],[6407,6600,"I thought I could if I tried."],[6600,6768,"But I learned love isn't like that."],[6807,6884,"Do you really want"],[6887,6960,"to marry me?"],[6971,7067,"I do."],[8143,8312,"My grandma once told me,"],[8331,8464,"when I meet someone I love,"],[8492,8623,"I should give them this necklace."],[8635,8731,"Lucian Russel,"],[8731,8884,"will you accept me?"],[8884,8979,"I promise—"],[8979,9131,"I'll never let you down."],[9143,9219,"Oscar,"],[9268,9415,"stop bothering my woman."]],"13":[[0,140,"Lucian."],[188,384,"Are you out of your mind?"],[687,831,"Can you even get it up?"],[1091,1203,"How do you know he can't?"],[1333,1426,"How do I know?"],[1569,1694,"Everyone here,"],[1719,1852,"even if they were blind,"],[1936,2044,"would know that"],[2155,2373,"all three of his legs don't work!"],[2446,2486,"What?"],[2508,2584,"You call him a man?"],[2726,2787,"Oscar Russel."],[2867,3021,"You want to slander a man's dignity"],[3023,3149,"with no proof?"],[3348,3428,"Then I could say—"],[3430,3621,"last time I kicked you—"],[3661,3740,"you loser."],[3837,3889,"Loser?"],[3935,3996,"Ridiculous."],[4038,4114,"I'm more than fine."],[4120,4216,"Let me tell you—"],[4216,4332,"on your birthday,"],[4332,4424,"your sister was in my bed,"],[4424,4520,"begging me to be..."],[4712,4848,"So Oscar really"],[4848,4992,"slept with Miss Quinn's sister."],[5040,5076,"Disgusting."],[5079,5271,"Playing with both Quinns' feelings—"],[5320,5435,"what a scumbag."],[5584,5748,"You finally slipped up."],[5792,5916,"B*stard!"],[5975,6167,"How could you do such a thing?"],[6312,6432,"Are you senile?!"],[6471,6584,"Passing the family head to"],[6592,6752,"Lucian Russel?!"],[6836,6964,"Are you trying to end"],[7007,7140,"our family bloodline?"],[7284,7383,"Disgrace!"],[7418,7496,"Guards!"],[7535,7598,"Take him—"],[7629,7737,"- Zack! - Grandpa!"],[7748,7794,"Zack!"],[7864,7923,"Zack!"],[7940,8064,"Doctor! Doctor!"]],"14":[[24,192,"Let go of me. Grandpa hasn't"],[192,352,"passed the family seal to Lucian yet."],[368,516,"It's still up in the air about"],[516,668,"who'll call the shots."],[760,812,"Oscar!"],[888,984,"Zack is in danger!"],[984,1076,"How can you say that!"],[1120,1248,"Get him to the hospital."],[1260,1348,"Hurry!"],[1348,1528,"Aurora, quit pretending."],[1588,1848,"Grandpa always knew you liked me."],[1848,1992,"Everyone hoped we'd marry,"],[2040,2204,"but you suddenly backed out."],[2739,2910,"I won't let you take Grandpa."],[2920,3076,"He's always doted on me most."],[3096,3188,"I'll take him myself."],[3260,3316,"Oscar."],[3360,3500,"Stop making trouble here."],[3500,3616,"Zack is in critical condition."],[3616,3772,"It's not the time to mess around!"],[3800,3848,"Aurora."],[3880,4036,"Think I don't know"],[4036,4188,"why you're staying by his side?"],[4248,4372,"Once Grandpa's gone,"],[4460,4496,"then,"],[4520,4732,"you'll get control over the family."],[4740,4804,"Oscar!"],[4840,4900,"Get out!"],[5000,5052,"Enough!"],[5160,5342,"You'll kill him if you keep this up."],[5375,5563,"I'll have someone take Zack to the hospital."],[5567,5714,"You wait here."],[5824,6047,"You two put on quite a show."],[6074,6180,"Someone might think"],[6224,6384,"you are truly in love."],[6560,6712,"We're not acting."],[6728,6922,"We are truly in love."],[7776,8020,"Lucian, I wish you two—"],[8112,8312,"a lifetime of happiness."]],"15":[[240,296,"Oscar Russel."],[324,432,"I've had enough with you."],[552,612,"You—"],[792,972,"Ah!"],[1192,1292,"My martial arts training—"],[1320,1452,"finally paid off."],[1680,1784,"You two—"],[1784,1908,"just wait and see!"],[2872,3048,"It's difficult for you, so..."],[3048,3180,"Let me clean you up."],[3328,3444,"No need."],[3444,3576,"I can do it myself."],[3576,3744,"I'm your fiancée."],[3744,3892,"It's my duty."],[3960,4084,"I don't want my fiancé—"],[4112,4316,"showing up looking filthy."],[5556,5732,"(Wasn't he paralyzed?)"],[5739,5883,"(Why's this thing still working?)"],[6384,6620,"Y-you wipe yourself."],[6707,6954,"I'll grab you a clean set of clothes."],[8040,8204,"Ah!"],[9064,9228,"Mr. Lucian, bad news!"]],"16":[[0,93,"Ah!"],[93,204,"-my face! -What's wrong, Oscar?"],[204,300,"My face!"],[528,583,"What's wrong?"],[597,659,"Oscar."],[729,805,"My face!"],[832,882,"Oscar."],[882,980,"My face!"],[980,1048,"Oscar,"],[1048,1183,"what's the matter?"],[1208,1296,"My face!"],[1327,1535,"Don't you know Oscar's allergic to peanuts?"],[1588,1648,"Allergic?"],[1700,1828,"Oscar, where's your medicine?"],[1828,1903,"I'll get it for you!"],[1939,2003,"My medicine—"],[2016,2192,"Aurora used to keep it."],[2203,2255,"Aurora!"],[2267,2344,"Aurora!"],[2376,2443,"Keep it?"],[2498,2534,"Hum!"],[2632,2735,"Everything from before—"],[2764,2955,"I've already tossed out."],[3016,3192,"Oh no, what do we do?"],[3200,3303,"Quit wailing—"],[3311,3435,"get me to a hospital!"],[4307,4532,"I almost died last night."],[4696,4803,"I'm sorry, okay?"],[4875,5011,"I really didn't mean it."],[5196,5267,"Save it."],[5267,5392,"But Aurora..."],[5447,5547,"she must've had medicine—"],[5579,5679,"and still didn't give me any."],[5775,6078,"I saw her with Lucian last night."],[6211,6404,"She won't really choose him, right?"],[6412,6479,"Impossible."],[6607,6756,"That cripple, Lucian…"],[6848,7015,"I'll head to the company now,"],[7087,7151,"and I'll make sure—"],[7220,7504,"neither the company nor the family back him."],[7548,7747,"In the end, Aurora will still marry me."],[8152,8258,"Slow down."],[9220,9300,"One more round?"],[9584,9720,"My legs are giving out."],[9764,9920,"You aren't \"useless\" at all."],[10040,10143,"The one unsatisfied last night—"],[10192,10268,"wasn't me."],[10423,10492,"Oh, stop."],[10515,10612,"Get up already."],[10615,10740,"I'll get you clothes."],[10776,10823,"Wait."],[10915,11020,"If you don't wash your clothes,"],[11020,11104,"I got you new ones."],[11641,11720,"Miss Aurora,"],[11723,11928,"Mr. Lucian Russel prepared ten custom gowns,"],[11968,12100,"two boxes of jewelry,"],[12123,12248,"three luxury cars,"],[12295,12412,"and two luxury villas."],[12428,12459,"You..."],[12507,12604,"what is all this?"]],"17":[[125,185,"Yes."],[1072,1172,"That's a lot."],[1400,1491,"It's nothing."],[1548,1683,"You might not believe this—"],[1719,1823,"but in all of Riverton"],[1880,1987,"my business empire"],[2039,2176,"has already surpassed my family's."],[2755,2867,"This is my entire fortune."],[3080,3148,"This bracelet"],[3176,3360,"is the token of the empire's ruler."],[3628,3679,"It's all yours."],[3743,3828,"(What?)"],[3884,4103,"(Riverton's underworld business empire)"],[4128,4321,"(is in my hands now?)"],[4479,4524,"What?"],[4579,4647,"You don't believe me?"],[4839,4920,"If it's from you,"],[5007,5075,"I believe it."],[5228,5335,"Pick a dress you like."],[5443,5471,"Mm."],[5479,5588,"Let's get our marriage license today."],[5667,5711,"Okay."],[5803,5871,"Send this file—"],[5888,6067,"to all employees' inboxes."],[6139,6203,"Manager Lewis."],[6423,6476,"Eh?"],[6520,6571,"Eh?"],[6643,6731,"Why are you avoiding me?"],[6823,6900,"I've got you something."],[6984,7087,"My brother Lucian"],[7156,7407,"got into some hot water recently."],[7564,7704,"If he comes to the company—"],[7759,7843,"just kick him out."],[7879,7995,"I'll take the heat."],[8464,8523,"Mr. Oscar."],[8728,8759,"This…"],[8795,8871,"isn't right."],[8979,9112,"As I said, just do it!"],[9184,9295,"Stop yapping."],[9364,9531,"Do you still want to be GM?!"],[9612,9792,"I really can't do this."],[10971,11112,"My grandpa is still unconscious,"],[11184,11323,"you don't believe me,"],[11368,11543,"but believe this f*cking file?"],[11612,11720,"Oh my god, he threw it!"],[11720,11904,"We only believe the family seal."],[12051,12123,"Back to work."],[12123,12195,"Yes."],[12379,12531,"You're all a bunch of b*stards!"],[12615,12784,"I'm about to be the family head!"],[12959,13124,"You'd better watch yourself."],[13308,13384,"Security!"],[13459,13611,"Escort this unauthorized person"],[13612,13668,"out of here."],[13668,13700,"Don't you dare!"],[13768,13859,"Don't you dare!"],[13884,14012,"You b*stard!"],[15763,15819,"Hello?"]],"18":[[475,551,"Starting today—"],[579,671,"you're my wife."],[712,755,"Okay."],[775,872,"I've waited"],[872,940,"so long for this."],[1016,1072,"Me too."],[1408,1435,"Hello?"],[1480,1519,"Mr. Russel,"],[1556,1700,"Oscar just left the company."],[1771,1871,"After hearing the news—"],[1871,1951,"he made a huge scene."],[1976,2039,"Ignore him."],[2092,2180,"If he comes again—"],[2228,2303,"keep me posted."],[2376,2412,"Yes, sir."],[3411,3535,"Why weren't you picking up?"],[3543,3603,"I was busy."],[3615,3675,"Let's drink."],[3715,3788,"Same place."],[4292,4324,"Drink!"],[4339,4467,"Drink up!"],[4500,4615,"Tonight's tab—"],[4635,4756,"is on me!"],[4952,5071,"Alright!"],[5071,5192,"Thank you, Oscar!"],[6047,6092,"Mr. Russel,"],[6107,6243,"your card declined."],[6256,6364,"Do you have another one?"],[6388,6464,"Watch your mouth!"],[6484,6584,"This is Oscar Russel."],[6604,6684,"Would he owe money?"],[6759,6807,"Oscar."],[6828,6915,"Show him again."],[6940,7012,"Smash him with cash!"],[7079,7143,"Watch."],[7535,7668,"Here it is."],[9071,9112,"Sorry."],[9112,9159,"Mr. Russel,"],[9176,9268,"all your cards are frozen."],[9320,9440,"Please use another one."],[9604,9687,"Impossible."],[9776,9851,"What happened?"],[9904,10064,"His family cut him off."],[10079,10164,"Oscar..."],[10200,10331,"Acting rich when you're broke?"],[10351,10435,"What's this?"],[10435,10523,"You want us to pay?"],[10576,10679,"This is ridiculous!"],[10823,11001,"It must be Aurora and Lucian's doing!"],[11168,11268,"How dare they!"],[11328,11440,"Freeze my cards?"],[12015,12087,"I'm at City Hall,"],[12143,12223,"no time for your crap."],[12279,12315,"Bye."],[12492,12656,"(Why's he at the City Hall?)"],[12656,12843,"(Is Aurora really marrying him?)"],[12936,12980,"Oscar,"],[13024,13084,"didn't you say"],[13084,13243,"you had Aurora in your palm?"],[13280,13505,"Now the things look pretty serious."],[13508,13546,"Shut up!"],[13596,13696,"If you don't act now—"],[13775,13812,"you'll—"],[13812,13915,"regret it later."],[13952,14024,"You're right."],[14096,14243,"I'm heading to the City Hall."],[14603,14659,"Oscar!"],[14675,14828,"Why beg that simp?"],[14828,14984,"Don't bow down to him!"],[14987,15059,"You're not going!"],[15063,15119,"What do you know?"],[15143,15175,"Get off!"],[16412,16512,"Starting today,"],[16540,16652,"I'll be calling you"],[16652,16955,"husband from now on."],[17008,17056,"Honey,"],[17163,17243,"actually,"],[17336,17503,"I have a secret to tell you."],[17512,17568,"What?"]],"19":[[575,636,"Aurora!"],[1080,1143,"Oscar."],[1200,1308,"What are you doing here?"],[1343,1380,"Aurora."],[1483,1596,"I came to apologize."],[1676,1783,"You're still mad at me"],[1783,1880,"'cause of the banquet, right?"],[2000,2071,"Forgive me, please."],[2496,2596,"I've already found"],[2628,2823,"someone who loves and cherishes me."],[2955,3048,"Give it up Aurora,"],[3100,3265,"stop roping Lucian into your games."],[3320,3443,"I know how you feel about me."],[3500,3547,"All these years—"],[3547,3652,"you've done so much for me."],[3715,3779,"Come back."],[3875,4015,"Was I not clear enough?"],[4047,4235,"I chose Lucian."],[4615,4743,"Aurora, are you serious?"],[4792,4892,"I've already given in,"],[4892,4967,"what more do you want?"],[5028,5128,"Do you really want to"],[5147,5292,"spend your whole life"],[5300,5400,"with a man in a wheelchair?"],[5520,5696,"Didn't you think things"],[5728,5820,"would end up"],[5820,5964,"like this when you chose Luna?"],[6052,6224,"I knew you still cared about me."],[6267,6428,"You're just jealous I'm with Luna."],[6504,6576,"I promise you—"],[6615,6815,"from now on I'll never see her again."],[6840,6895,"Alright?"],[6968,7051,"I'm afraid—"],[7151,7268,"someone's going to be heartbroken."],[7564,7687,"What did you say?"]],"20":[[191,264,"For her,"],[356,500,"you'd give up on me?"],[1064,1148,"Why are you here?"],[1296,1459,"What did you promise me back then?"],[1540,1737,"You said you'd dump that b*tch Aurora—"],[1771,1880,"and be with me forever."],[1880,2055,"Make me the lady of the Russel family."],[2087,2180,"Did you forget?"],[2300,2376,"All these years,"],[2451,2523,"how much money"],[2523,2696,"have you squeezed outta Zack?"],[2783,2980,"Now that you've lost your fortune—"],[3035,3167,"you wanna dump me?"],[3260,3311,"Luna Quinn."],[3379,3479,"As your brother—"],[3479,3592,"I'm warning you one last time."],[3660,3828,"Stay away from me."],[3960,4115,"Everybody knows"],[4115,4307,"Aurora and I grew up together."],[4415,4503,"And you—"],[4571,4720,"you're just a schemer."],[4739,4856,"How could you marry me?"],[4920,5047,"Calling me a schemer?"],[5184,5260,"Oscar Russel."],[5292,5475,"Where is your f*cking conscience?!"],[5760,5939,"You're just an adopted daughter."],[6124,6252,"Know your place."],[6311,6367,"Adopted?"],[6571,6723,"I've been in your family for decades."],[6815,7004,"I thought you all accepted me."],[7171,7284,"Adopted is adopted."],[7348,7492,"You're just delusional."],[7595,7743,"You're f*cking disgusting!"],[8012,8123,"How dare you hit me!"],[8151,8204,"Guards!"],[8295,8428,"Take her away!"],[8507,8587,"Don't touch me!"],[8735,8792,"Oscar Russel!"],[8800,8976,"You'll pay for this!"],[8976,9112,"Aurora, you saw it."],[9135,9295,"There's nothing between us."],[9307,9468,"She's delusional about me."],[9631,9851,"We aren't interested in your boring drama."],[9976,10068,"Let's go."],[10076,10123,"Go home."],[10331,10492,"I just pitied her because"],[10531,10620,"she was adopted."],[10643,10723,"How could I like her?"],[10723,10748,"I—"],[10884,10976,"I like you."],[11028,11100,"Give me another chance."],[11348,11428,"I'm warning you—"],[11515,11643,"stay away from my wife."],[11776,11892,"I'm done being polite!"],[11979,12071,"You cripple—"],[12120,12268,"how dare you talk to me?"]],"21":[[0,115,"You cripple!"],[136,279,"How dare you talk to me!"],[579,728,"Watch your filthy mouth!"],[787,988,"Aurora, of all men to choose—"],[1000,1148,"you chose this cripple?"],[1167,1308,"All he does is rot at home,"],[1319,1416,"begging Grandpa for pity."],[1435,1548,"He's got nothing against me!"],[1596,1807,"You're that confident in yourself?"],[1848,1896,"Lucian."],[1928,2051,"Let others talk if they want—"],[2096,2207,"but don't fool yourself."],[2312,2483,"What can a useless man give her?"],[2523,2583,"Do you really think—"],[2583,2748,"she married you out of love?"],[2832,3003,"She's just trying to spite me!"],[3128,3239,"I'll say it again—"],[3320,3464,"I chose Lucian Russel."],[3464,3584,"I love Lucian Russel."],[3584,3732,"You mean nothing to me!"],[3756,3796,"You—"],[3892,3943,"Fine."],[4052,4171,"I'll show you right now—"],[4232,4371,"who can be your husband!"],[4492,4564,"Let go of me!"],[4584,4684,"I'm taking her today!"],[4700,4767,"Let's see if this cripple—"],[4775,4884,"dares say no!"],[4903,4952,"Guards!"],[4992,5128,"Help Mr. Oscar calm down!"],[5267,5315,"Ah!"],[5703,5803,"Ah, that hurts!"],[5811,5843,"Oscar."],[5943,6064,"There's no medicine for regret."],[6128,6252,"For Grandpa's sake,"],[6300,6492,"at our wedding in three days,"],[6528,6615,"if you decide to attend,"],[6676,6784,"you'll be received politely."],[6868,6920,"What?"],[7031,7115,"You and Lucian—"],[7151,7315,"already set the date?"],[7340,7428,"You b*tch!"],[7779,7879,"You make your choice,"],[7900,8040,"so don't blame me for mine!"],[8076,8171,"Block my path—"],[8195,8371,"and I'll destroy you!"]],"22":[[24,184,"Honored guests, please take your seats."],[184,308,"The wedding is about to begin."],[492,584,"Congrats to you both."],[624,732,"A perfect match."],[760,860,"A blessed union."],[884,964,"From now on—"],[976,1088,"the Russel family depends on you."],[1132,1188,"That's right."],[1228,1328,"You're both young and capable."],[1336,1428,"We elders—"],[1440,1618,"will fully support you."],[1752,1832,"Sir, madam,"],[1832,1888,"you flatter us."],[1936,1992,"Ah."],[2052,2188,"We've all—"],[2188,2324,"always thought highly of you."],[2348,2436,"It's just"],[2456,2624,"there's a certain Oscar Russel."],[2632,2748,"A spoiled playboy."],[2788,2856,"Alas..."],[2896,3092,"We were all angry—"],[3164,3284,"but couldn't speak up."],[3336,3380,"Sigh."],[3416,3528,"A failure of a man."],[3540,3648,"Why bring him up?"],[3660,3688,"Here."],[3724,3856,"Let's toast the newlyweds!"],[3880,3920,"Here!"],[3960,4052,"Happy wedding day!"],[4076,4180,"Congratulations."],[4184,4276,"Congratulations."],[4292,4364,"Happy wedding day!"],[4612,4784,"A failure of a man?"],[5068,5220,"I don't know about that."],[5772,5924,"You old cronies—"],[6020,6260,"better think before you speak."],[6380,6468,"Oscar."],[6528,6696,"Today's my wedding with Lucian."],[6736,6864,"If you're here to cause trouble—"],[6900,7028,"I'd suggest you think again."],[7080,7136,"Ooh—"],[7136,7236,"I'm so scared."],[7244,7332,"I'm so scared."],[7364,7468,"Scared that this cripple—"],[7468,7612,"might jump and bash my knees."],[7864,7952,"On our big day..."],[7980,8128,"I won't embarrass you too much."],[8136,8224,"See yourself out."],[8268,8440,"You think I'm scared?"],[8528,8628,"I told you:"],[8660,8776,"I'm here today—"],[8787,9050,"to take back what's mine!"],[9084,9296,"Aurora will marry me!"],[9312,9384,"And I—"],[9516,9696,"will be the Russel family head."]],"23":[[120,212,"Oscar Russel."],[231,368,"Do you know where you are?"],[384,468,"Such reckless words..."],[512,612,"Are you insane?"],[628,708,"Oscar Russel"],[732,908,"is trying to take the bride!"],[920,984,"Oscar Russel!"],[1028,1152,"Was the lesson at city hall—"],[1172,1304,"not enough for you last time?"],[1364,1528,"It's just a few bodyguards."],[1652,1788,"Who doesn't have some?"],[2084,2148,"Oscar Russel!"],[2176,2232,"Don't be reckless."],[2300,2432,"We elders are still here！"],[2464,2508,"Exactly."],[2536,2636,"You weren't chosen,"],[2655,2828,"and the new head is about to wed—"],[2864,2980,"yet you're still causing trouble!"],[3028,3204,"They're not officially married."],[3300,3380,"In the end—"],[3412,3548,"you'll be thanking me."],[3664,3736,"Otherwise,"],[3748,3840,"the Russel family"],[3892,4126,"will fall at the hands of a dead man."],[4172,4304,"Who're you calling a dead man?"],[4368,4508,"Watch your mouth."],[4652,4760,"Can't you see?"],[4800,4908,"This guy"],[4940,5080,"is not only a cripple,"],[5112,5188,"but has also"],[5200,5380,"been poisoned for years."],[5408,5564,"If I hadn't come today,"],[5620,5732,"this wedding—"],[5812,5964,"would've turned into a funeral!"],[5992,6112,"Cough, cough."],[6252,6352,"Lucian is dying?"],[6388,6524,"How do you know all that?"],[6548,6592,"Don't tell me"],[6604,6744,"you poisoned your brother?"],[6752,6904,"Does that even matter now?"],[6952,7000,"Tch."],[7032,7180,"He's about to die."],[7328,7532,"Will this wedding still go on?"],[7660,7716,"Aurora."],[7768,7932,"If you change your mind now—"],[7992,8200,"I'll marry you right here."],[8344,8444,"Keep dreaming."]],"24":[[0,128,"Keep dreaming."],[248,396,"Your opinion doesn't matter."],[432,584,"I'm sure the elders here,"],[640,748,"for the sake of family ties,"],[748,860,"have their own concerns."],[860,944,"At this point,"],[984,1104,"are you going to back out?"],[1132,1208,"Aurora,"],[1260,1444,"we understand how you feel."],[1448,1520,"But—"],[1556,1804,"the Russel family isn't just any family."],[1820,1948,"The relationships here"],[1976,2112,"are very complicated."],[2124,2200,"In my opinion,"],[2208,2336,"let's not beat around the bush."],[2360,2492,"Zack hasn't woken up yet,"],[2512,2672,"the Russel family won't fall."],[2692,2760,"This wedding—"],[2764,2864,"might as well be canceled."],[2960,3092,"I don't care what happens to the Russels,"],[3104,3184,"I, Aurora,"],[3184,3312,"have chosen Lucian,"],[3336,3488,"and I will only marry him."],[3524,3720,"How did Lucian manage to bewitch you?"],[3784,3992,"He's dying, and you still want him?"],[4004,4100,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[4100,4192,"look closely."],[4224,4360,"Aurora Quinn is treating"],[4392,4571,"the Russel family's future as a joke."],[4608,4752,"Zack once told me,"],[4771,5080,"whoever I choose will inherit the Russel family."],[5104,5172,"What?"],[5207,5384,"Now you won't even listen to him?"],[5392,5528,"Don't use Grandpa to pressure me."],[5560,5717,"He hasn't even woken up yet."],[5732,5948,"Don't marry that dying man."],[5956,6100,"Grandpa wouldn't approve,"],[6124,6256,"and neither do I."],[6288,6368,"I think"],[6400,6556,"Oscar has a point."],[6568,6640,"As I see,"],[6640,6764,"your choice is irresponsible."],[6804,6912,"And you, Lucian,"],[6928,7108,"you're hiding a serious illness."],[7132,7248,"You hear that?"],[7284,7396,"F*ck off now."],[7556,7632,"Oscar,"],[7652,7772,"do you really think"],[7780,7896,"I don't know the tricks"],[7920,8008,"you've been pulling?"]],"25":[[48,88,"Ah!"],[96,167,"How did he—"],[304,343,"How—"],[412,512,"How is that possible?!"],[544,659,"You should be a cripple!"],[712,835,"How can you stand now?"],[864,996,"Disappointed, aren't you?"],[1167,1203,"Ah—"],[1211,1248,"This—"],[1283,1439,"I knew you were secretly"],[1440,1553,"poisoning me."],[1596,1746,"I've laid low all these years"],[1748,1883,"quietly countering your tricks—"],[1887,1980,"waiting for this day."],[2003,2100,"For you to expose yourself."],[2283,2392,"Impossible!"],[2451,2564,"Everyone!"],[2628,2676,"He—"],[2692,2796,"he's faking it!"],[2816,2951,"He won't last long!"],[2964,3067,"Don't believe him!"],[3112,3203,"Oscar,"],[3228,3352,"your schemes have failed."],[3356,3424,"There's nothing"],[3452,3552,"you can do now."],[3675,3732,"Lucian"],[3732,3852,"may hold on for a while,"],[3852,3988,"but not for a lifetime!"],[4035,4240,"I request that Lucian be cast out,"],[4260,4384,"left to die on his own!"],[4392,4553,"Only I can lead the Russel family"],[4556,4628,"to glory!"],[4667,4720,"Oscar,"],[4784,4924,"Lucian already said"],[4952,5064,"he's perfectly healthy."],[5147,5267,"As for the poisoning,"],[5267,5367,"we haven't punished you,"],[5379,5572,"you still dare to fight for heirship?!"],[5615,5720,"The Russel family's future"],[5728,5856,"is none of your concern."],[5984,6152,"Lucian and I will handle it."],[6235,6335,"Please, leave."],[6392,6459,"How could this be—"],[6595,6679,"How could this be?!"],[6751,6835,"Mr. Stone of Zenith Group is here!"]],"26":[[0,68,"Mr. Stone!"],[76,191,"You're finally here."],[235,364,"Mr. Stone of Zenith Group."],[451,651,"I don't recall inviting you."],[712,816,"The Russel family and we,"],[816,1003,"the Zenith Group, are long-time rivals—"],[1035,1159,"and old friends."],[1200,1272,"What?"],[1283,1474,"Aren't I allowed to come congratulate you?"],[1503,1564,"Mr. Stone,"],[1616,1755,"today is my wedding."],[1760,1898,"If you want to talk business,"],[1960,2071,"please choose another day."],[2096,2228,"Sir Russel isn't here."],[2271,2400,"If I want to talk business,"],[2460,2698,"it's not your turn, little brat."],[2823,2880,"Mr. Stone,"],[2912,3035,"show some respect."],[3083,3167,"He is the"],[3167,3315,"new head of the Russel family."],[3347,3471,"I'll be honest with you—"],[3556,3702,"your Russel family's eldest,"],[3703,3771,"Oscar Russel,"],[3771,3971,"has agreed to let Zenith Group"],[3975,4248,"acquire Russel Group."],[4320,4407,"In other words,"],[4460,4575,"your Russel Group,"],[4575,4850,"will soon belong to Zenith Group!"],[4860,4943,"What?!"],[4979,5270,"Oscar holds such a large share—"],[5343,5626,"isn't this just handing over the Russels?"],[5696,5906,"No wonder Oscar is so confident today,"],[5947,6084,"looks like the Russels are changing hands."],[6135,6203,"Oscar Russel,"],[6235,6328,"how could you?!"],[6356,6537,"What's wrong with joining Zenith Group?"],[6568,6731,"It's good to lean on a big tree."],[6792,6959,"It'll make our group stronger—"],[6979,7035,"isn't that better?"],[7056,7215,"Most importantly,"],[7240,7320,"from now on,"],[7331,7587,"Zenith will call the shots."],[7643,7720,"As for the head of Russels,"],[7792,8000,"naturally, it'll be Oscar."],[8084,8159,"Oscar,"],[8192,8398,"you're not qualified for headship."],[8412,8540,"What right do you have?"],[8620,8635,"You—"],[8751,8887,"Your Russel Group"],[8887,9090,"will soon be ours."],[9143,9366,"I think I have every right to decide."],[9407,9650,"Mr. Stone of Zenith has made his move."],[9651,9740,"And your move?"],[9984,10079,"How could you—"]],"27":[[224,372,"Dear elders!"],[372,448,"how could you—"],[448,624,"Sorry, Aurora."],[624,748,"In business,"],[748,959,"it's survival of the fittest."],[967,1067,"Frankly,"],[1067,1172,"it's Aurora's fault—"],[1172,1243,"she didn't choose"],[1243,1319,"the right groom."],[1319,1367,"Exactly."],[1367,1448,"Otherwise,"],[1448,1551,"how could the Russel family"],[1551,1664,"end up like this?"],[1664,1755,"Right."],[1764,1855,"Yes."],[1855,1951,"That's right."],[1976,2067,"Fine, fine."],[2076,2260,"Lucian and I already figured out"],[2287,2351,"you couldn't"],[2351,2487,"have done all this on your own."],[2496,2683,"Since the traitor's revealed himself,"],[2707,2851,"it's not all bad—"],[2851,2996,"it's a good chance for me"],[2996,3103,"to purge the Russel family."],[3116,3279,"What good are words?"],[3279,3443,"Let's compare our strengths first."],[3503,3552,"Aurora,"],[3552,3724,"if you dump him now,"],[3724,3784,"I might—"],[3784,3884,"just give you a chance"],[3884,3992,"to stay by my side."],[3992,4111,"In your dreams."],[4164,4260,"Oscar,"],[4260,4379,"let me remind you—"],[4420,4556,"the company's current chairman"],[4556,4647,"is Zack."],[4664,4820,"With just one word from him,"],[4820,4979,"everything you promised Mr. Stone"],[4996,5096,"becomes void."],[5103,5235,"Don't use Sir Russel"],[5235,5352,"to pressure people."],[5367,5456,"Sir Russel"],[5456,5611,"is still in the hospital."],[5639,5735,"Exactly."],[5735,5928,"The matter's settled—"],[5928,5992,"why bother"],[5992,6111,"struggling in vain?"],[6111,6275,"Didn't you hear the elders?"],[6275,6375,"Grandpa isn't here,"],[6400,6495,"what can you do?"],[6495,6607,"Bring him here"],[6640,6771,"to scold me right now?"],[6828,6935,"Young man,"],[6935,7143,"don't be so arrogant."],[7143,7300,"If I didn't know"],[7304,7435,"Sir Russel was in a coma,"],[7487,7684,"would I even come?"],[7843,7971,"Aurora,"],[7971,8104,"Lucian,"],[8104,8228,"did you hear that?"],[8228,8404,"I have the advantage now,"],[8428,8559,"you can't do anything to me!"],[8579,8779,"If you bring Grandpa here,"],[8779,8951,"I, Oscar Russel,"],[8951,9184,"will give up immediately—"],[9184,9271,"and to you both,"],[9271,9423,"bow my head in apology."],[9423,9468,"Good."],[9468,9492,"Good."],[9492,9635,"That's what I was waiting for."],[9671,9815,"Open your eyes wide—"],[9876,10035,"and see who's here."]],"28":[[220,312,"What..."],[312,387,"He's awake?!"],[387,444,"Oscar!"],[444,596,"What did you just say?"],[651,708,"Grandpa!"],[708,819,"How are you..."],[956,1003,"Sir Russel."],[1003,1167,"When did you wake up?"],[1175,1296,"Zack has been awake for a while."],[1351,1532,"He hid it until now..."],[1564,1648,"So you traitors..."],[1648,1796,"Would expose yourselves."],[1796,1928,"Now he has seen..."],[1928,2055,"your true faces."],[2132,2207,"Grandpa!"],[2207,2296,"It's not like that!"],[2323,2432,"Let me explain—"],[2435,2519,"Begone!"],[2551,2635,"The Russels won't recognize"],[2635,2751,"such an ungrateful traitor!"],[2803,2883,"From today on..."],[2939,3148,"you have no place in this family."],[3228,3332,"Ryan Stone..."],[3332,3456,"I'm warning you."],[3460,3571,"As long as I am"],[3571,3647,"still living and breathing,"],[3675,3852,"nothing this ungrateful child says..."],[3856,3960,"has any weight!"],[4164,4203,"Mr. Stone..."],[4203,4260,"Help me!"],[4260,4307,"Mr. Stone!"],[4307,4415,"Y-you..."],[4415,4479,"Oscar Russel..."],[4507,4539,"This..."],[4539,4707,"this isn't what we talked about!"],[4707,4788,"Ah?"],[4828,5020,"Sir Russel!"],[5020,5167,"Sir Russel!"],[5211,5300,"It was him!"],[5320,5367,"It was—"],[5367,5464,"Oscar Russel!"],[5464,5600,"He's the one who tricked us!"],[5647,5752,"It's him!"],[5752,5856,"That's right!"],[5856,5915,"Sir Russel..."],[5915,6067,"This brat was the culprit!"],[6067,6192,"He deceived all of us!"],[6192,6352,"Do you think I'm blind?"],[6352,6412,"It truly has"],[6412,6528,"nothing to do with us, Sir Russel!"],[6528,6643,"You betrayed the family..."],[6643,6776,"and caused up irreparable harm."],[6815,6931,"You still want to come back?"],[7023,7151,"Get out, all of you!"],[7223,7300,"Sir Russel!"],[7331,7431,"Mr. Stone, help me!"],[7431,7512,"If you just help me..."],[7512,7607,"I'll agree to anything!"],[7607,7684,"Get lost!"],[7684,7743,"Mr. Stone!"],[7779,7840,"I have"],[7840,7928,"the Russel Group's"],[7928,7984,"top-secret files."],[7984,8076,"And product formulas."],[8076,8164,"If you help me,"],[8164,8348,"I'll give them all to you."],[8348,8451,"Help me!"]],"29":[[32,124,"Oscar Russel."],[124,312,"You'd hand the Russel Family's"],[327,448,"centuries-old secrets to our rivals?!"],[471,641,"How can you stoop so low?"],[856,1091,"You… you b*stard!"],[1119,1200,"Oscar,"],[1200,1406,"are you set on angering Grandpa to death?"],[1451,1710,"You were the ones who left me with nothing."],[1771,1896,"You showed no mercy—"],[1912,2067,"don't blame me for doing the same."],[2176,2280,"If that's the case—"],[2416,2507,"I think…"],[2507,2700,"we can still negotiate."],[2700,2816,"Mr. Stone,"],[2816,2987,"what do you mean?"],[2996,3217,"If my Zenith Group"],[3220,3379,"went all in..."],[3443,3600,"against the Russel Group,"],[3600,3720,"we would be"],[3720,3875,"evenly matched."],[4047,4217,"So you insist on protecting that b*stard—"],[4300,4539,"and going to war with us?"],[4539,4652,"If Oscar"],[4652,4860,"gives me what I want,"],[4860,5011,"then the Russel Group"],[5017,5267,"cannot beat me for sure."],[5275,5420,"You—!"],[5420,5500,"That's right."],[5500,5675,"Mr. Stone"],[5675,5875,"is the CEO of Zenith Group."],[5928,6084,"And also"],[6084,6256,"a member of the Underground Business Union."],[6339,6476,"He's got plenty of means."],[6500,6640,"That's my trump card"],[6640,6876,"for going head-to-head with you."],[7095,7287,"Have you heard of Ruler A?"],[7368,7451,"Ruler A?"],[7515,7715,"He's the ruler of the entire Underground"],[7715,7815,"Business Union."],[7815,7884,"He's not someone"],[7884,8031,"you can casually talk about!"],[8064,8228,"Don't tell me…"],[8228,8323,"the 'A'..."],[8340,8500,"is the one in your name?"],[8571,8648,"Wrong."],[8692,8771,"The 'A'..."],[8915,9089,"stands for Aurora."],[9113,9379,"Hahaha!"],[9379,9492,"Don't tell me—"],[9492,9748,"she's the underground ruler?"],[9843,9907,"Lucian,"],[9923,10020,"are you out of your mind?"],[10059,10187,"Spouting nonsense like this?"],[10187,10331,"If you don't believe me,"],[10456,10540,"take a look at this."]],"30":[[248,432,"Isn't this just a worthless bracelet?"],[432,559,"You wanna scare me with this?"],[744,872,"This…"],[988,1067,"Lucian Russel."],[1159,1216,"Aurora Quinn."],[1296,1488,"You two should learn your place."],[1488,1567,"Apologize to me and Mr. Stone."],[1712,1855,"You b*stard!"],[1919,2035,"You set me up!"],[2035,2144,"You set me up!"],[2144,2228,"You set me up!"],[2228,2403,"You f*cking set me up!"],[2583,2796,"I was blind,"],[2807,2928,"fooled by that Oscar Russel"],[2928,3096,"and did such stupid thing."],[3235,3432,"Please don't begrudge me."],[3464,3664,"Please forgive me."],[3832,4075,"Aurora is the ruler of the underground?"],[4132,4296,"Mr. Stone, you must be mistaken."],[4435,4584,"Aurora?"],[4584,4715,"That's impossible."],[4715,4775,"Mr. Stone."],[4775,4939,"I grew up with her."],[4939,5115,"I know exactly what she's capable of."],[5115,5224,"There's no way she is!"],[5260,5367,"Get out!"],[5643,5843,"What if I told you"],[5843,6152,"the real ruler is Lucian?"],[6384,6535,"Oscar Russel."],[6571,6651,"Did you really think"],[6651,6720,"all these years"],[6720,6956,"I've just been your puppet?"],[7251,7340,"Ryan Stone, hear my order."],[7420,7556,"I command Zenith Group"],[7556,7728,"to be under the Russels from now on."],[7768,7912,"Support the Russels wholeheartedly."],[7920,8007,"Yes, sir!"],[8092,8240,"Thanks for your trust!"],[8695,8776,"Lucian."],[8815,8895,"I was wrong."],[8940,9020,"Give me another chance."],[9043,9123,"Just one."],[9251,9304,"I was wrong."],[9304,9331,"I'm sorry."],[9331,9451,"Just once."],[9464,9543,"Guards!"],[9604,9664,"Lucian."],[9664,9723,"Take him away."],[9723,9964,"Lucian!"],[9992,10100,"Forgive me this once!"],[10151,10228,"Lucian!"],[10276,10384,"Forgive me this once!"],[11768,11804,"Slow down."],[11804,11943,"Be careful with our baby."],[11984,12056,"I know."],[12168,12264,"Sir, please!"],[13275,13584,"He brought this on himself."],[13584,13675,"Let's go."]]}